        <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          Looking for affordable SEO services for small business? I specialize in comprehensive SEO optimization that helps your website rank higher on Google and increase organic traffic. My affordable SEO services include on-page optimization, off-page strategies, technical SEO, and local SEO to ensure your business gets the visibility it deserves.
        </p>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          Unlike agencies that offer generic packages, I provide affordable SEO service for small business with customized strategies tailored to your specific needs. Every affordable SEO service I offer is designed to deliver measurable results and help you outrank your competitors without breaking your budget.
        </p>
